{"type": "article", "id": 17705, "title": "翻转吊灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-18T06:40:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606141850Jkt3VFPu09OwLDUi.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一组翻转吊灯，三块完全一样的条形灯板在交接处留了一条缝，让灯光透过缝隙透射出来而不是直射，避免伤害眼镜。从远处看，这种灯的光线非常柔和，几盏灯错落排列，像垂吊下来的花瓣。光线是聚拢向下的，更适合需要在正下方使用的人。有白、灰两种颜色可选，售价 119 欧元。<a href=\"http://www.oato.nl/2015_invert.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144759GTXKmz6gdqBs8CYM.jpg\" width=\"465\" height=\"700\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.50537634\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144800ufna3V67I9WcjbLY.jpg\" width=\"472\" height=\"629\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.33262712\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144800IBEL8AC2K01yltTQ.jpg\" width=\"472\" height=\"629\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.33262712\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261448004XLdyPkFcSNwHZOp.jpg\" width=\"472\" height=\"629\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.33262712\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}